{
  "message": "fuzz(repair-evidence-ledger): 18 seeds for previously-uncovered event types\n\nExisting 18 seeds covered ~10 of the 22 EvidenceEventType variants.\nAdd 18 seeds covering the remaining variants plus structural edges:\n\n  newly-covered event types:\n    * SnapshotAdvanced (mvcc snapshot tracking)\n    * BackpressureActivated (write-back pressure threshold cross)\n    * DirtyBlockDiscarded (txn-abort discards dirty state)\n    * DurabilityPolicyChanged (overhead-ratio adaptive policy)\n    * RefreshPolicyChanged (per-group symbol refresh policy)\n    * MergeProofChecked (valid + invalid-with-rejection_reason)\n    * MergeApplied (committed-with-merged-writes)\n    * MergeRejected (proof variant did not validate)\n    * PolicySwitched (adaptive policy mode change)\n    * ContentionSample (periodic stats sample with all rates)\n    * SymbolRefresh (repair-symbol generation bump)\n\n  structural / parser-edge cases:\n    * block_range present alongside an event-specific detail\n    * blank-line / whitespace-only / tab-only separators between records\n    * CRLF line endings (\\r strip path)\n    * max u64 in timestamp_ns / block_group / detail fields\n    * 10-record block (multi-line scaling)\n    * multi-line block interleaving 3 distinct new event types\n\n109K runs / 11s post-seed surface no crashes.",
